{
  "stem": "19352.1",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They took me over from this terrible hell on Earth, ghetto, to a-- the place, I believe that someplace is a better place for to be free.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And that time, I realized that I have to survive, I have to survive because otherwise, I cannot live like that anymore.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And this, I think, made me survive.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But it didn't take too long.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They came over and they're also [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] take away the music instruments, the fur coats, the linen, the silverware, paintings-- everything what they thought that we don't need it anymore.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We didn't know that they were going to do like that.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "People came back from-- it was an uprising in Treblinka and people came back to the ghetto, told-- told us that this is the last solution, this is the solution of the Germans, that they will burned us and-- and killed us and to try-- and he want to organize us against the Germans to we uprising there.",
      "word_count": 58
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But we were sick and-- and hungry.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We didn't believe him that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "My father told him, go away, don't tell those people.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They have to live.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It's impossible.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "If-- if the world will know about it, they would not allow to do it.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But we were alone.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Nobody helped us.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My childhood before the war was fantastic.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Of course you go to school, you have to study.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But after school, especially, we went to school six-- six days a week, Saturdays also.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But after that wintertime, I ski and I skate and it was beautiful.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I came home-- they didn't tell me when I have to go home-- come home.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
